OpenGTA2
========


Quick Start
-----------

 * Download GTA2INSTALLER.ZIP (http://www.rockstargames.com/classics/) into
   ./gta2/
 * Execute ./gta2/unpack-gta2installer.sh, this will verify the downloaded
   GTA2INSTALLER.ZIP and unpack it as far as possible
 * Execute ./gta2/GTA2.exe with wine
 * Install GTA2 into $directory
 * Change into the ./gta2 directory and install-gta2.sh $directory, this will
   copy all neede files from the GTA2 installation into the gta2 directory.
   You can uninstall the original GTA2 after this step


